description: Normalized log2ratio protein abundance estimates for the TCGA Ovarian JHU Proteome study (PDC Study ID: PDC000113) were obtained via the PDC API quantDataMatrix endpoint. TThese data are part of the CPTAC2 Retrospective project. More information on the pipeline and the results generated by it can be found here: https://pdc.cancer.gov/data-dictionary/harmonization.html
